- cs.CL (Computation and Language): Topic modeling is a subfield of natural language processing, which falls under the cs.CL category. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): Topic modeling is also used in information retrieval to improve search results. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Topic modeling is a technique used in AI for text analysis and understanding.
